measurements.description: Twenty-six slightly cupped flowers on two up to 97-cm upright staked inflorescences; sepals ivory overlaid centrally red-pink; petals ivory, midline red-pink, suffused near midline; lip ivory, midlobe picotee, dark red-pink distally, side lobes edged pink, callus yellow; column ivory overlaid and spotted dark pink, anther cap white; substance firm; texture matte.
